

**Operating System:** Amazon Linux AMI  

| Service   | EC2 Instance | Purpose                  | Default Port |
|-----------|--------------|--------------------------|--------------|
| Jenkins   | jenkins      | CI/CD pipeline execution | 8080         |
| SonarQube | sonar        | Code quality analysis    | 9000         |
| Nexus     | nexus        | Artifact repository      | 8081         |
| Tomcat    | tomcat       | Application deployment   | 8080         |


- **22 (SSH):** Restrict to your IP only  
- **8080:** Jenkins / Tomcat  
- **9000:** SonarQube  
- **8081:** Nexus
